methods.name: values
methods.description: Returns an array containing the constants of this enum class, in the order they are declared.

methods.name: valueOf
exceptions: IllegalArgumentException - if this enum class has no constant with the specified name
methods.description: Returns the enum constant of this class with the specified name. The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an enum constant in this class. (Extraneous whitespace characters are not permitted.)

enum_constants.name: SUCCEED
enum_constants.description: Forces the event to cause the position check to succeed.

enum_constants.name: DEFAULT
enum_constants.description: The results of Mob.checkSpawnRules(LevelAccessor, MobSpawnType) and Mob.checkSpawnObstruction(LevelReader) will be used to determine if the check will succeed. If this is being called from a spawner, the Mob.checkSpawnRules(LevelAccessor, MobSpawnType) call will be skipped if any SpawnData.CustomSpawnRules are present.

enum_constants.name: FAIL
enum_constants.description: Forces the event to cause the position check to fail.
